beer.beer_description: A really overly nice hoppy brown. Munich, amber and midnight wheat malts bring a slightly sweet and nutty backbone, while Chinook, Cascade & Columbus hops nod to the pine forests of the great white north…and bring some citrus along for the ride!

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
